<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #9b59b6;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 16px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 15px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h2>You’ve Been Invited to a New Activity!</h2>
    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p><strong><%= @inviter.name %></strong> has invited you to join the activity: <strong><%= @activity.activity_name %></strong> on Voxxy.</p>
    <p>Click below to log in and view your new activity:</p>

    <!-- ✅ This should now work properly -->
    <a href="<%= @login_link %>" class="button">Log in to Voxxy</a>

    <p>Looking forward to seeing you there!</p>
    <p>– The Voxxy Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>